long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bulldog Book is a Chrome extension that allows you to see residential college info in the Facebook profile of Yale students.

For more information, visit http://f03lipe.github.io/bdbook
